## Steps

@row steps-example
  @card .ghost
    Code:
    ```
    @steps workflow
      @step
        ## Draft
        Write markdown and directives.
      @end step

      @step
        ## Preview
        Run `marque serve .`.
      @end step

      @step
        ## Publish
        Upload `dist/`.
      @end step
    @end steps workflow
    ```
  @end card

  @card .ghost
    Result:

    @steps workflow
      @step
        ## Draft
        Write markdown and directives.
      @end step

      @step
        ## Preview
        Run `marque serve .`.
      @end step

      @step
        ## Publish
        Upload `dist/`.
      @end step
    @end steps workflow
  @end card
@end row steps-example

