## Hero and section

@row hero-section-example
  @card .ghost
    Code:
    ```
    @hero .accent launch
      # Ship docs faster
      Keep writing in markdown, add structure only when useful.
    @end hero launch

    @section .ghost why
      ## Why this works
      Less boilerplate, more content velocity.
    @end section why
    ```
  @end card

  @card .ghost
    Result:

    @hero .accent launch
      # Ship docs faster
      Keep writing in markdown, add structure only when useful.
    @end hero launch

    @section .ghost why
      ## Why this works
      Less boilerplate, more content velocity.
    @end section why
  @end card
@end row hero-section-example

